

App Class : main function

main function:
Sets up scanner to input file then sends scanner
to Functions.output which returns proper output.
Also asks for the name of the output file and displays
proper messages to let the User know.

Functions Class : output function

output function:
Sets up a string builder to go line by line in the input
and replace all of the word "utilize" with "use". Returns
the string value of the string builder which is later printed
into the output file through main. It is redirected to remain
in the ex45 folder.